{
  "id": "adv_event_2203_01_04",
  "title": "並び立つ歌姫のフルリール 4話 私に下さい……！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The next day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃんと瑠依ちゃん、遅いね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku-chan and Rui-chan‚ they're late…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "せやなぁ、{user}さんとこ行ってから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ since they went to {user}-san's place.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "一時間くらい経つけど……大丈夫やろか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's been about an hour… Is everything okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "{user}さんなら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it's {user}-san‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "絶対二人の背中を押してくれるよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "he will definitely support both of them!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "でも、二人はいいの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But are you both okay with it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんが雫ちゃんと新ユニットを組んでも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if Rui-chan forms a new team with Shizuku-chan‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "うーん……最初聞いた時は、複雑だったけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I first heard about it‚ I felt conflicted.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "でも、瑠依ちゃんにはもっともっと輝いてほしいし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I want Rui-chan to shine even more.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "うちも同じ気持ちや……でも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I feel the same way… But",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんの方が、もっと気持ちは複雑そうやね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-chan seems to have more complicated feelings.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "それって……どういうこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you mean by that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんは、トリエルのこと大事に想ってるからなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's because Rui-chan cares deeply about TRINITYAiLE.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃんと一緒にステージに立つの、随分悩んでたんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She was quite hesitant about standing on stage with Shizuku-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "自分がステージに立つ時は、トリエルの一員としてだけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When she stands on stage‚ it's only as a member of TRINITYAiLE.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "それ以外には考えられないって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She can't imagine anything else besides that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "だから、昨日の夜、うちら三人で",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ last night‚ the three of us",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "長いこと話し合ってん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "had a long discussion.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "最後には、瑠依ちゃんの、トリエルの可能性を",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the end‚ Rui-chan agreed that it was an opportunity",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "広げるチャンスだって、瑠依ちゃんも納得したの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "to expand TRINITYAiLE's possibilities.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そんなことがあったんだ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn't know such a thing happened…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんも、二人も、凄く悩んだんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Both Rui-chan and Shizuku-chan were really troubled‚ huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.9666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4766.666666600003
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、みんな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ everyone!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.6333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "待ってくれてたの？　私達のことはいいから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Were you waiting for us?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "先にレッスン始めてって言ったのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I told you to start the lesson without us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "二人のことが気になって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We were worried about both of you‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "レッスンに身が入らないよ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so we couldn't focus on the lesson~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それで雫ちゃんと瑠依ちゃん、一緒に組めるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ you can form a team together‚ Shizuku-chan and Rui-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、許してくれた？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did {user}-san give the permission?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "せやなぁ。早く教えて？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Tell us quickly‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "え、えっと……その……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ um… Well…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "雫、私のことは気にしなくても……言っていいのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku‚ you don't have to worry about me… You can say it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "……る、るる……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…R-Rururu…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2203_01_04-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "るーるる？　ハミング？　なんの歌？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rurururu? Humming? What song is that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ちゃうって、雫ちゃん、唇震えてるやんか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ no‚ Shizuku-chan‚ your lips are trembling.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
